### Test Organizer Sales and Revenue Reports API Endpoints

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@authToken = Bearer YOUR_ORGANIZER_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### 1. Get Comprehensive Sales Report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-sales
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 2. Get Sales Report with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-sales?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 3. Get Monthly Revenue for Current Year
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-revenue/monthly/2024
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 4. Get Event Performance Metrics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-events/performance
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 5. Get Event Performance with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-events/performance?startDate=2024-06-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 6. Get Daily Sales Breakdown
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-sales/by-period?periodType=daily&startDate=2024-09-01&endDate=2024-09-30
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 7. Get Weekly Sales Breakdown
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-sales/by-period?periodType=weekly&startDate=2024-09-01&endDate=2024-09-30
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 8. Get Monthly Sales Breakdown
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-sales/by-period?periodType=monthly&startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-12-31
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 9. Get Payment Methods Breakdown
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-payments/methods
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 10. Get Payment Methods with Date Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-payments/methods?startDate=2024-08-01&endDate=2024-09-30
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 11. Get Event Summary Dashboard
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-events/summary
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 12. Test Invalid Period Type (Should Fail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-sales/by-period?periodType=invalid
Authorization: {{authToken}}

###

### 13. Test Unauthorized Access (Should Fail - Remove Authorization Header)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/my-sales

###

### 14. Original Organizer Report by ID (For comparison)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Reports/organizer/YOUR_ORGANIZER_ID_HERE
Authorization: {{authToken}}

